name: Windsor Brick Oven Pizza & Subs
description: Windsor Brick Oven Pizza & Subs in Windsor, Colorado is a locally owned and operated pizzeria, proudly serving the greater Windsor, Colorado area. We take pride in only serving the freshest ingredients! Our vegetables are sliced and diced daily, our dough is made fresh everyday, and our cheeses are grated daily to ensure the best taste!
